The paper focuses on image representation learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of genetic algorithms for optimization suggests a machine learning approach (cs.LG). The task of content-based image retrieval involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the use of data-driven feature learning suggests an artificial intelligence approach (cs.AI).
